name: Cobalt dragon
description: In this work, two important elements of more than one era of Asian art are combined: the dragon is the most recognizable silhouette in the world of Asian art, personifying wisdom and strength. And cobalt is a chemical element used to create a pigment, the use of which has taken more than one era around the world, bringing with it the uniqueness of color and clarity of lines. Now before you digitalized: colors, textures and motive of the drawing of those times ... the choice is yours.
